title: Lung Ta
description: Vegetarian diner, small floor seating area with traditional low tables and outdoor terrace. Menu changes everyday, typically contains miso soup, sushi, tempura vegetable and/or tofu steak. Profits go to assisting former Tibetan political prisoners. Set menu costs around 130 in Nov 2010. A la carte menu mains around 80-100. Set menu typically includes some items with eggs, but they will prepare without eggs if you ask. Location is 500m south of the main bus stand,.shortly after ladies venture.
